Subject: netfilter: nf_tables: initialize registers in nft_do_chain()
Patch-mainline: v5.18-rc1
Git-commit: 4c905f6740a365464e91467aa50916555b28213d
References: CVE-2022-1016 bsc#1197227

Initialize registers to avoid stack leak into userspace.

Fixes: 96518518cc41 ("netfilter: add nftables")
Signed-off-by: Pablo Neira Ayuso <pablo@netfilter.org>
Acked-by: Michal Kubecek <mkubecek@suse.cz>

---
 net/netfilter/nf_tables_core.c | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

--- a/net/netfilter/nf_tables_core.c
+++ b/net/netfilter/nf_tables_core.c
@@ -162,7 +162,7 @@ nft_do_chain(struct nft_pktinfo *pkt, void *priv)
 	struct nft_rule *const *rules;
 	const struct nft_rule *rule;
 	const struct nft_expr *expr, *last;
